          </div>

          <!-- Hidden abstract block -->
          <div class="abstract hidden">
            <p>The resolvent operator for the confined time of arrival operator is obtained explicitly, and the transcendental characteristic equations for the eigenvalues reported earlier are reproduced.</p>
          </div>
